                        With an intuitive dashboard, veterinarians can monitor patient history, update treatment plans, and track progress for every case, ensuring comprehensive animal care. The portal also supports collaboration and knowledge-sharing among vets through specialized forums and webinars.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Key Features List -->
