                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 justify-content-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-calendar-check fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">Easily manage and schedule appointments with a user-friendly interface.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 justify-content-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-clipboard fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">Access detailed case files, including medical history, diagnostic reports, and treatment notes.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 justify-content-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-comments fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">Communicate directly with farmers and pet owners through secure messaging for timely updates and advice.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 justify-content-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-graduation-cap fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">Stay informed with access to educational content, webinars, and peer-reviewed articles on the latest in veterinary science.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 justify-content-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-network-wired fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">Join a community of vets, share knowledge, and collaborate on complex cases via our professional forums.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

