                        <i class="fa fa-tractor me-2"></i>Farmer Portal
                    </h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify;">
                        The <strong>Farmer Portal</strong> is designed to simplify the lives of farmers, providing seamless access to veterinary services, an extensive Agrovet hub, and valuable educational resources. It empowers farmers to ensure the health and productivity of their livestock and pets through a user-friendly and comprehensive platform.
                    </p>
