                        Farmers can easily book vet appointments, order essential supplies, and receive expert guidance on animal care best practices. The portal also offers a range of articles and video tutorials, covering topics from disease prevention to livestock nutrition, ensuring you have all the tools you need to thrive.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Key Features List -->
                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 justify-content-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-calendar-check fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">Effortlessly schedule vet appointments to keep your animals in optimal health.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 justify-content-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-shopping-basket fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">Browse and purchase from our Agrovet hub, offering a variety of high-quality animal supplies and products.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3 justify-content-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-lightbulb fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
