                            <i class="fa fa-chart-line fa-2x text-success me-3"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">Monitor your farm’s progress with helpful insights and tips to boost productivity and animal welfare.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <!-- Call to Action Button -->
                    <a href="/Farmer/Index" class="btn btn-lg btn-success px-4 py-2 shadow">Get Started as a Farmer</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section id="about" class="my-5" style="background-image: url('/img/connect.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height: 70vh; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); border-radius: 10px;">
            <div class="row text-center text-dark">
                <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-success mb-4">
                        <i class="fa fa-info-circle me-2"></i>About Us
                    </h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify;">
                        <strong>Vet Connect</strong> is a leading platform dedicated to revolutionizing the relationship between farmers, pet owners, and veterinarians. Our goal is to create a seamless, integrated space where veterinary services, educational resources, and high-quality products are accessible to all, ensuring the best care for animals.
