                            <i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">An integrated marketplace offering high-quality pet and livestock products, from nutrition to health supplies.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-left align-items-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">A platform built on trust, ensuring all veterinarians are certified and all products meet high-quality standards.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-left align-items-left">
                            <i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i>
                            <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">A community-driven initiative, fostering connections between farmers, pet owners, and veterinarians.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <p class="lead mt-4" style="line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify;">
                        Join us on this journey as we strive to improve animal health, strengthen communities, and make veterinary care accessible to all. Together, we can make a lasting impact on animal welfare across the globe.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Us Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="my-5" style="background-image: url('/img/connect.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height: 70vh; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); border-radius: 10px;">
            <div class="row text-center text-dark w-100">
                <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-success mb-4">
                        <i class="fa fa-envelope me-2"></i>Contact Us
                    </h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify;">
                        We’d love to hear from you! Whether you have a question, feedback, or need assistance with our services, feel free to get in touch. Our team is here to help you connect with the best veterinary care and resources.
                    </p>
                    <p class="lead mb-4" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify;">
                        Simply fill out the form below and we’ll get back to you as soon as possible. Let’s work together to create a healthier world for your pets and livestock.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Display Success/Error Message -->
                    @if (TempData["MessageStatus"] != null)
                    {
                        <div id="alert-box" class="alert alert-@TempData["AlertType"] alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                            <strong>@TempData["MessageStatus"]</strong>
                            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
                        </div>
                    }

                    <!-- Contact Form -->
                    <form class="w-100 mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;" method="post">
                        @Html.AntiForgeryToken() <!-- CSRF Token -->

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="message" class="form-label">Message</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
                        </div>

                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success w-100 shadow">
                            <i class="fa fa-paper-plane me-2"></i>Send Message
                        </button>
                    </form>

                    <!-- JavaScript to auto-dismiss the alert -->
                    <script>
                            // Check if the alert-box exists
                        const alertBox = document.getElementById('alert-box');
                        if (alertBox) {
                            // Automatically fade out the alert after 5 seconds (5000 milliseconds)
                            setTimeout(() => {
                            let alert = new bootstrap.Alert(alertBox);
                            alert.close();
                        }, 5000); // Adjust the time as needed (currently set to 5 seconds)
                        }
                    </script>

                    <p class="lead mt-4" style="line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify;">
                        You can also reach us via email at
                        <a href="mailto:michaelotienokasuku@gmail.com" class="text-success fw-bold">michaelotienokasuku@gmail.com</a>
                        or call us at
                        <a href="tel:0742644460" class="text-success fw-bold">0742644460</a>. We look forward to hearing from you!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQs Section -->
    <section id="faqs" class="my-5" style="background-image: url('/img/connect.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height: 80vh; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); border-radius: 12px;">
            <div class="row text-dark w-100">
                <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-success text-center mb-4">
                        <i class="fa fa-question-circle me-2"></i>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-center fs-5 mb-5" style="line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;">
                        Find answers to common queries about our platform, services, and policies.
                    </p>

                    <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="faqAccordion">
                        <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                    How do I book an appointment with a vet?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <strong>Booking an appointment is easy!</strong> Log in to your Vet Connect account, browse the available veterinarians, select one that matches your needs, and choose an available time slot. Confirm your booking, and you will receive a confirmation email with all the details. Need help? Watch our step-by-step video tutorial in the Help section.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                    What services do you offer?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    We offer a wide range of veterinary services, including:
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Consultations and check-ups</li>
                                        <li>Vaccinations and routine immunizations</li>
                                        <li>Surgical procedures</li>
                                        <li>Nutrition and diet consultations</li>
                                        <li>Emergency care for both pets and livestock</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    For a detailed list of all services, visit our <a href="/Services" class="text-success">Services Page</a>.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                    Can I reschedule or cancel my appointment?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    Yes, you can reschedule or cancel your appointment through your account. Simply log in, go to "My Appointments," select the booking you want to change, and choose a new time or cancel altogether. <strong>Note:</strong> Cancellations must be made at least 24 hours before the appointment to avoid charges.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                    How do I contact a vet in case of an emergency?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    For emergencies, you can contact our 24/7 emergency hotline at <strong>0742644460</strong>. Alternatively, visit the <a href="/EmergencyServices" class="text-success">Emergency Services page</a> for more options, including urgent virtual consultations and immediate on-site visits.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                    Do you offer virtual consultations?
                                </button>
                            </h2>
                            <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    Yes! We offer virtual consultations via video or phone call for minor issues or follow-ups. Simply select "Virtual Consultation" when booking your appointment and ensure your internet connection is stable for a seamless experience.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
